OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA breezy
OL,6,Fnight with most areas remaining dry
OL,7,Fwith longest clear spells in the east.
OL,8,FChance of a few showers across the
OL,9,FDerbyshire hills. Feeling cooler
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunshine and chance of showers
OL,13,Ffor Sunday, these potentially heavy. A
OL,14,Fwindy day with temperatures mostly
OL,15,Faround average, but overnight ground
OL,16,Ffrost is possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
